    public class homePage
extends androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
    Class: homePage This is a class that composes the home-page of the app The home page initialize and displays the list of experiments It inflate the layout for the experiment's fragment It allows user to add a new experiment by clicking a floating button

    Fragment, Firebase
